# Data Definitions

## AWS Credentials â€” Required Before Any Athena or S3 Access

Credentials expire every **4 hours**. Before running any script or notebook that touches Athena or S3, refresh them:

```bash
source scripts/refresh_aws_credentials.sh
```

This sets:
- `AWS_ARTIFACT_TOKEN` â€” CodeArtifact token from `beehero` domain (us-east-1)
- `UV_INDEX_BEEHERO_PYPI_USERNAME` â€” `aws`
- `UV_INDEX_BEEHERO_PYPI_PASSWORD` â€” the token above

Use `source` (not `bash`) so the exports apply to your current shell session.

